<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Lowongan Nganggur</title>

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    *{
      margin:0;
      padding:0;
      box-sizing:border-box;
      font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
    }

    body{
      min-height:100vh;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, #1e293b 0%, transparent 30%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, #334155 0%, transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #020617, #0f172a);
      overflow-x:hidden;
      color:white;
      padding:30px 15px;
      position:relative;
    }

    /* Background pattern */
    .pattern{
      position:absolute;
      inset:0;
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size:35px 35px;
      animation:movePattern 15s linear infinite;
      z-index:0;
    }

    @keyframes movePattern{
      from{
        transform:translate(0,0);
      }
      to{
        transform:translate(-35px,-35px);
      }
    }

    /* Floating text */
    .floating-text span{
      position:absolute;
      color:white;
      opacity:0.04;
      font-size:0.9rem;
      animation:float 20s linear infinite;
      white-space:nowrap;
      z-index:0;
    }

    @keyframes float{
      from{
        transform:translateY(110vh);
      }
      to{
        transform:translateY(-20vh);
      }
    }

    /* Main card */
    .card{
      position:relative;
      z-index:2;
      width:100%;
      max-width:850px;
      background:rgba(15,23,42,0.85);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
      border-radius:24px;
      padding:40px;
      box-shadow:
        0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5),
        inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    }

    .badge{
      display:inline-block;
      padding:8px 16px;
      border-radius:999px;
      background:rgba(239,68,68,0.15);
      color:#fca5a5;
      font-size:0.85rem;
      margin-bottom:20px;
      border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.25);
    }

    h1{
      font-size:3rem;
      line-height:1.1;
      margin-bottom:8px;
      font-weight:700;
    }

    .company{
      color:#94a3b8;
      font-size:1rem;
      margin-bottom:30px;
    }

    .job-box{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border-radius:18px;
      padding:20px;
      margin-bottom:25px;
    }

    .job-title{
      font-size:1.5rem;
      font-weight:700;
      margin-bottom:12px;
      color:#f8fafc;
    }

    .info{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));
      gap:15px;
      margin-top:15px;
    }

    .info div{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      padding:14px;
      border-radius:14px;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    }

    .info span{
      display:block;
      font-size:0.8rem;
      color:#94a3b8;
      margin-bottom:5px;
    }

    h2{
      font-size:1.1rem;
      margin-top:30px;
      margin-bottom:15px;
      color:#f1f5f9;
    }

    ul{
      list-style:none;
    }

    li{
      margin-bottom:12px;
      line-height:1.6;
      position:relative;
      padding-left:22px;
      color:#cbd5e1;
    }

    li::before{
      content:"•";
      position:absolute;
      left:0;
      color:#38bdf8;
      font-size:1.2rem;
    }

    .apply{
      margin-top:35px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0ea5e9,#2563eb);
      padding:22px;
      border-radius:18px;
      line-height:1.7;
      box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(37,99,235,0.25);
    }

    .apply strong{
      display:block;
      margin-bottom:10px;
      font-size:1.1rem;
    }

    .footer{
      margin-top:25px;
      text-align:center;
      font-size:0.9rem;
      color:#94a3b8;
      opacity:0.8;
    }

    @media(max-width:700px){

      .card{
        padding:25px;
      }

      h1{
        font-size:2rem;
      }

      .job-title{
        font-size:1.2rem;
      }

      li{
        font-size:0.95rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="pattern"></div>

  <div class="floating-text">
    <span style="left:8%; animation-delay:0s;">rebahan</span>
    <span style="left:25%; animation-delay:4s;">scroll</span>
    <span style="left:45%; animation-delay:8s;">overthinking</span>
    <span style="left:65%; animation-delay:12s;">nganggur</span>
    <span style="left:85%; animation-delay:16s;">deadline</span>
  </div>

  <div class="card">

    <div class="badge">
      LOWONGAN TERBARU 2026
    </div>

    <h1>LOWONGAN NGANGGUR</h1>

    <div class="company">
      PT. Mencari Cinta Sejati Tbk.
    </div>

    <div class="job-box">

      <div class="job-title">
        POSISI: REBAHAN SPECIALIST (FULL-TIME)
      </div>

      <div class="info">
        <div>
          <span>Penempatan</span>
          Kamar Masing-Masing (WFH)
        </div>

        <div>
          <span>Gaji</span>
          Wawasan Baru Tentang Bermacam-macam Stress
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <h2>DESKRIPSI PEKERJAAN</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Menjaga kestabilan kasur & bantal.</li>
      <li>Memantau pergerakan langit-langit kamar.</li>
      <li>Scrolling media sosial tanpa tujuan.</li>
      <li>Memikirkan "Mau jadi apa?" sambil tetap rebahan.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>KUALIFIKASI UTAMA</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Pendidikan: Minimal pernah sekolah (tidak diutamakan).</li>
      <li>Pengalaman: Minimal 1 tahun nunda pekerjaan (Procrastinator Pro).</li>
      <li>Tahan menatap HP 12 jam nonstop.</li>
      <li>Tahan mental ditanya tetangga "Kerja di mana?"</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>FASILITAS & BENEFIT</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Jam kerja fleksibel (bebas bangun kapan saja).</li>
      <li>Bebas tekanan bos (tekanan dari diri sendiri).</li>
      <li>Dress code: Kaos oblong pudar & celana kolor legendaris.</li>
      <li>Tidak perlu laporan harian.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="apply">
      <strong>CARA MELAMAR</strong>

      Tidak perlu kirim CV. Matikan alarm besok pagi,
      tarik selimut, lanjutkan nganggur Anda!

      <br><br>

      <em>
        *KUOTA TERBATAS! Khusus Anda yang benar-benar tidak niat kerja.*
      </em>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      © 2026 • Dibuat dengan rasa malas yang konsisten
    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
